## Additional Notes

If you use notification groups that include **both iOS and Android devices**, some
features (such as Android notification channels and grouping) may not behave consistently.

Refer to the official documentation for further details:
[Companion App Notification Docs](https://companion.home-assistant.io/docs/notifications/notifications-basic#sending-notifications-to-multiple-devices)

